  <main class="page">
    <div class="container page-wrap">
      <h1>About Top Gear Decide</h1>
      <p class="lead">Honest, evidence-based guidance for the food, supplements and drinks you put in your body.</p>

      <p>Top Gear Decide started with a simple frustration: shopping for supplements, pantry staples and drinks had become an exhausting maze of conflicting star ratings, influencer hype and label claims that told you everything except whether a product was actually worth buying. We built this site to cut through that noise.</p>

      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>Our team researches, compares and ranks products across the categories that matter most to how you eat and fuel your day — supplements, pantry essentials and everyday drinks. Every guide is organized to answer the questions real shoppers ask first: which one is best, which one is the smartest value, and which one fits my specific diet or goal.</p>

      <h2>How We Evaluate Products</h2>
      <p>We combine hands-on research with structured comparison. That means looking closely at ingredient quality, nutrition and macros, third-party testing and certifications, taste and mixability, value per serving, and the long-term reliability signals from verified buyers. When a product underperforms or simply does not justify its price, we say so — a recommendation only means something if we are willing to leave products off the list.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>We prioritize what affects real results and everyday enjoyment over marketing buzzwords.</li>
        <li>We weigh price against quality and nutrition, not in isolation.</li>
        <li>We update our guides as new products launch and prices shift.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Independence</h2>
      <p>Top Gear Decide earns commissions through affiliate links, including the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. Those commissions never influence our rankings or opinions. We choose which products to feature based on merit, and you can read the full details on our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> page.</p>

      <h2>A Note on Health</h2>
      <p>Our content is for general information only and is not medical or nutritional advice. Supplements and dietary products affect people differently — always check the label and talk to a qualified healthcare professional before starting anything new, especially if you are pregnant, nursing, taking medication or managing a health condition.</p>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>Have a product you'd like us to cover, or feedback on a guide? We'd love to hear from you — head over to our <a href="/contact">Contact</a> page and send us a note.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us by Email</h2>
      <p>You can also reach us directly by email:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>General questions &amp; feedback: <a href="mailto:info@topgeardecide.com">info@topgeardecide.com</a></li>
        <li>Advertising &amp; affiliate partnerships: <a href="mailto:affiliate@topgeardecide.com">affiliate@topgeardecide.com</a></li>
      </ul>
